Name: Skedaddle Out The Dungeon
About the game: Gameplay: Skedaddle Out The Dungeon is an indie developed Rogue-like. Fight your way through randomly generated dungeons against the many monsters that inhabit it. Collect unique items, coins, and bombs to help obliterate anything that stands in your way! This is my first game and I hope you all will enjoy it :) Features: Procedural dungeon generation 4 Unique Bosses 5 Unique Enemies 5 Unique Active Items Randomized shop
